{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882793925,"sessionID":"ses_28524d66cffePG3Ba89bHGEPE1","part":{"id":"prt_d7adceed5001Ok3AgaSDoJ9RAI","messageID":"msg_d7adce5a1001mjCIXVU6qWeofp","sessionID":"ses_28524d66cffePG3Ba89bHGEPE1","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_4ce15a39c339443aa2e01d53","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md","limit":50,"offset":1155},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1155: \n1156: ---\n1157: \n1158: # AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n1159: \n1160: - **AR ID**: AR-039\n1161: - **Module**: pkg\n1162: - **Language**: Go\n1163: - **Size**: L\n1164: \n1165: ## 概述\n1166: \n1167: 本任务为 `agentcube` 项目的 router、store 和 picod 三个核心包编写单元测试，覆盖架构设计、数据结构、API 契约、错误处理和测试策略。\n1168: \n1169: ## 架构\n1170: \n1171: ### router 包\n1172: \n1173: **核心组件：**\n1174: \n1175: | 组件 | 文件 | 职责 |\n1176: |------|------|------|\n1177: | `Router` | `server.go` | 主路由器，管理 HTTP 服务器、后端池、认证、中间件 |\n1178: | `BackendPool` | `backend.go` | 后端服务器池，支持路径/Header 路由 |\n1179: | `Backend` | `backend.go` | 单个后端服务器，含健康检查状态 |\n1180: | `RouteHandler` | `route.go` | 路由匹配逻辑 |\n1181: | `Proxy` | `proxy.go` | 请求代理到后端 |\n1182: | `HealthChecker` | `health.go` | 后端健康检查 |\n1183: | `RateLimiter` | `ratelimit.go` | 请求速率限制 |\n1184: | `Authenticator` | `auth.go` | Token 认证 |\n1185: | `SessionManager` | `session.go` | 会话管理（内存实现） |\n1186: | `JWTManager` | `jwt.go` | JWT 令牌管理 |\n1187: | `JWTMiddleware` | `jwt_middleware.go` | JWT 认证中间件 |\n1188: | `Metrics` | `metrics.go` | 请求指标收集 |\n1189: | `Logger` | `logging.go` | 请求日志中间件 |\n1190: \n1191: ### store 包\n1192: \n1193: **核心组件：**\n1194: \n1195: | 组件 | 文件 | 职责 |\n1196: |------|------|------|\n1197: | `Store` | `store.go` | 抽象存储接口 |\n1198: | `ValkeyStore` | `store_valkey.go` | Valkey 客户端实现 |\n1199: | `RedisStore` | `store_redis.go` | Redis 客户端实现 |\n1200: \n1201: ### picod 包\n1202: \n1203: **核心组件：**\n1204: \n\n(Showing lines 1155-1204 of 3131. Use offset=1205 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\n---\n\n# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-039\n- **Module**: pkg\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: L\n\n## 概述\n\n本任务为 `agentcube` 项目的 router、store 和 picod 三个核心包编写单元测试，覆盖架构设计、数据结构、API 契约、错误处理和测试策略。\n\n## 架构\n\n### router 包\n\n**核心组件：**\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775882793906,"end":1775882793923}}}}
